{
  "stem": "2533.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They came in and all that, so they was stationed there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I don't remember exactly how many days, and then for a-- for a week or a fortnight, not just there but all around, and then they withdrew.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They probably went to that River Bug, and that's where they stopped.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And it was a lawless time.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The hooligans, they were-- they were not just, you know, whatever they could lay their hands on, stealing, and-- and even they got from the Polish army, from the one who were left running or something, the ammunition and all that.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And a delegate from the town went to Chelm to ask the Germans to come in to have a little bit of order because we were hiding in the cellars.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We were afraid to go out because it was a lawless period.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So-- but when the Germans came, [BACKROUND NOISE] we didn't realize that it's going to be even worse.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It wasn't lawless with the Germans.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It wasn't so bad right away, but it started off then.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When they first arrived, they took away the, how shall I say, they took away some teachers.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They took away the mayor of the town.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They took away prominent people, even priests.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they saw that they are going to be hostages.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they will return, but nothing will happen, but nobody will harm the-- the military-- the German military.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But we never saw them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That stopped.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Oh, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, yes, yes, Polish",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because a lot of the Jewish young people went with the Russians.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "When the Russians withdrew, they went with them, yes.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, but then it was all right when the German arrived, but they were starting to take things away, whatever we-- we-- we had, like from the business and all that.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So--",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
